  "title": "Litigation Lawyer (Debt Recovery)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Kelvin Chia Partnership is a medium-size law firm headquartered in Singapore with a regional presence in South East Asia. We are looking for dynamic and motivated individuals to join us as an Associate in our Debt Recovery Department.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Admission as an Advocate & Solicitor of Singapore</p><p>- 1- 2 years’ experience in Debt Recovery</p><p>- Able to deal with files from instruction to resolution</p><p>- Skilled in developing existing clients and generating new business</p><p><strong>Newly called applicants are welcome to apply as ample guidance, training and support will be provided.</strong></p><p>Interested applicants are invited to email their resume stating current and expected salaries to kcpcareers@kcpartnership.com</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
